ent reports, and recommend mitigation rules to\nfacilitate automated security training.\n+ Tech stack: Python, Wazuh, Docker, Nginx, ModSecurity, FastAPI, LangGraph, Qdrant, Linux\nWORK EXPERIENCE\nGENERAL ERA DIGITAL SOLUTION JOINT STOCK COMPANY\nJanuary 10, 2024 - April 10, 2024\n« Security Infrastructure: Participated in deploying and configuring security services and internal\ninfrastructure to enhance the company's defense posture.\n« Cloud Security: Implemented and managed cloud protection measures using Cloudfiare (WAF, DNS,\nand DDoS mitigation) to safeguard web applications.\n« System Hardening: Assisted in optimizing server security and ensuring compliance with basic\nsecurity standards.\nSKILLS\nCybersecurity & Risk\n+ Log analysis, event monitoring, alert triage\n+ SIEM: Wazuh, ELK Stack\n+ Basic risk identification and security assessment\n+ Understanding of security controls and mitigation strategies\nSystems\n& Networking\n« Linux (Ubunty, Kali), Windows Server\n+ TCP/IP, CCNA fundamentals\nProgramming\n& Tools\n« Python, Bash (basic scripting & automation)\n» Tools: Elastic, Burp Suite, Cloudflare\nFrameworks & Knowledge\n« ISO/IEC 27001 & 27002 (basic understanding)\n« NIST Cybersecurity Framework (Identify, Protect, Detect, Respond)\n+ OWASP Top 10 (Web Application Security Risks)\n» MITRE ATT&CK Framework (basic mapping of threats and techniques)\nACHIEVEMENTS AND CERTIFICATE\n« Connect and Protect: Networks and Network Security - Google Certificate\n« Top 4 - FIA CTF CYBERSUS 2025\n« Certified Cybersecurity Educator Professional (CCEP) - Red Team Leader\n« Certified Red Team Operations Management (CRTOM) - Red Team Leader\n« Ethical Hacker - Cisco Academy\n» CCNA: Switching, Routing, and Wireless Essentials - Cisco Academy\nADDITIONAL INFORMATION\n« English: Intermediate\n+ Willing to work shifts\n+ Strong self-learning mindset and adaptability	Python\nFastAPI\nMachine Learning\nDocker	new	2026-05-15 12:39:46.909131+00	2026-05-15 12:40:01.304359+