ver.\nPROJECT\nLearn English Website (Personal project)\n07/2025\n- Present\nFullStack Developer\nDescription:\n• Built a vocabulary learning web application with authentication, topic-based learning, quizzes, and progress tracking.\n• Designed and tested RESTful APIs using ASP.NET Core (Web API), Vue.js frontend, JWT authentication, and Postman, deploying a scalable backend.\n• Enhanced learning experience with analytics and intelligent vocabulary suggestions, enabling progress tracking and personalized review.\nNumber of members: 1\nTechnology in use: Vue.js, JavaScript, Html, Css, Boostrap, .NET 8 (ASP.NET Core), RESTful API, Postman\nGitHub Repository: https://github.com/PhanDuongQuoc/Learn-English-Project.git\nReal Love Wedding Website (Freelancer)\n09/2024\n- 01/2025\nFullstack Developer\nDescription:\n• Developed a wedding photography e-commerce website with booking and gallery management features.\n• Implemented backend with ASP.NET Core (.NET 8) & SQL Server and styled UI with SCSS for a responsive, modern design.\n• Delivered project for client within 3 months, ensuring smooth deployment and usability.\nNumber of members: 2\nTechnology in use: Html, Scss, ASP.NET Core (.NET 8), SQL Server\nGitHub Repository: https://github.com/PhanDuongQuoc/ReaLove_Wedding_NetCore.git\nTECHNICAL SKILL\nFrontend: Vue.js, Html, CSS, SCSS, Boostrap, Tailwind\nBackend: ASP.NET Core MVC, Web API\nDatabase: SQL Server, My SQL, MongoDB\nTools: Git, SVN,TortoiseSVN, Docker, Postman, Visual Studio, Visual Studio Code\nEnglish: B1, good communication	Java\nJavaScript\nSQL\nREST API\nDocker\nGit\nBack-end Development	new	2026-05-14 18:51:31.324333+00	2026-05-14 18:51:46.163259+00	cv_pdf	Phan-Duong-Quoc-Software-Developer.pdf	processed	rule_based	0.92	synced	\N	2026-05-14 18:51:31.427932+00	{"summary": "Software Developer \\ud83d\\udcde0839 295 061 \\u2709phanduongquoc111@gmail.com \\ud83d\\udd17https://www.linkedin.com/in/phanduongquoc111/ \\uf3c5213 Tang Nhon Phu, Quan 9 \\uf05ahttp