26	Backend / Full-stack Developer	Remote/contract Backend / Full-stack Developer role focused on building modern web applications with Node.js, Spring Boot, React, RESTful APIs, and SQL/NoSQL databases. The position emphasizes scalable systems, AI-powered features, performance optimization, and collaboration with distributed teams in a remote, agile environment.	Node.js\nSpring Boot\nReact\nExpress.js\nREST API\nJavaScript\nSQL\nNoSQL\nPostgreSQL\nMongoDB\nMySQL\nSQL Server\nJWT-based authentication\nAI/LLM APIs\nPrompt engineering\nAI agent design\nArtificial Intelligence\nJava\nGit\nGitHub\nVersion Control\nBack-end Development\nFull-stack Development\nScalable systems\nAsynchronous processing workflows\nPerformance optimization\nSoftware engineering best practices\nDebugging\nProblem solving\nSoftware testing\nDeployment\nCollaboration\nUser experience optimization\nRecommendation systems\nIntelligent user workflows\nAI-powered features\nSoftware Development\nAgile Environments	draft	2026-05-14 18:51:16.807969+00	2026-05-14 18:51:16.81527+00	Design, develop, and maintain scalable backend and full-stack web applications.\nBuild and integrate RESTful APIs using Node.js, Express.js, or Spring Boot.\nDevelop responsive frontend interfaces using ReactJS and modern JavaScript frameworks.\nCollaborate with cross-functional teams to deliver high-quality software solutions.\nImplement AI-powered features, recommendation systems, or intelligent user workflows.\nOptimize application performance, scalability, and user experience.\nParticipate in debugging, testing, deployment, and feature enhancement activities.\nWork with SQL and NoSQL databases including PostgreSQL, MongoDB, and MySQL.\nMaintain clean, maintainable, and well-documented code following software engineering best practices.\nUse Git/GitHub workflows for version control and collaborative development.	Hands-on experience with Node.js, Express.js, Java Spring Boot, or backend web development.\nExperience building full-stack applications using ReactJS and RESTful APIs.\nUnderstanding of scalable application architecture and asynchronous processing workflows.\nFamiliarity with SQL and NoSQL databases such as PostgreSQL, MongoDB, MySQL, or SQL Server.\nExperience integrating AI/LLM APIs or intelligent application features is a strong advantage.\nKnowledge of authentication systems such as JWT-based authentication.\nStrong debugging, problem-solving, and performance optimization skills.\nAbility to work independently and collaboratively in remote environments.\nGood written and verbal communication skills.	Job Title\nBackend / Full-stack Developer\nJob Type\nRemote / Contract\nJob Summary\nWe are looking for a passionate Backend / Full-stack Developer with hands-on experience building modern\nweb applications using Node.js, Spring Boot, React, RESTful APIs, and SQL/NoSQL databases.\nThe ideal candidate has experience developing scalable systems, integrating AI-powered features, and\nbuilding user-focused applications with optimized performance and modern software engineering\npractices.\nYou will collaborate with distributed teams to design, develop, and improve backend services and full-stack\nplatforms in a remote and agile environment.\nKey Responsibilities\nDesign, develop, and maintain scalable backend and full-stack web applications.\nBuild and integrate RESTful APIs using Node.js, Express.js, or Spring Boot.\nDevelop responsive frontend interfaces using ReactJS and modern JavaScript frameworks.\nCollaborate with cross-functional teams to deliver high-quality software solutions.\nImplement AI-powered features, recommendation systems, or intelligent user workflows.\nOptimize application performance, scalability, and user experience.\nParticipate in debugging, testing, deployment, and feature enhancement activities.\nWork with SQL and NoSQL databases including PostgreSQL, MongoDB, and MySQL.\nMaintain clean, maintainable, and well-documented code following software engineering best\npractices.\nUse Git/GitHub workflows for version control and collaborative development.\nRequired Skills & Qualifications\nHands-on experience with Node.js, Express.js, Java Spring Boot, or backend web development.\nExperience building full-stack applications using ReactJS and RESTful APIs.\nUnderstanding of scalable application architecture and asynchronous processing workflows.\n•\n•\n•\n•\n•\n•\n•\n•\n•\n•\n•\n•\n•\n1\n\nFamiliarity with SQL and NoSQL databases such as PostgreSQL, MongoDB, MySQL, or SQL Server.\nExperience integrating AI/LLM APIs or intelligent application features is a strong advantage.\nKnowledge of authentication systems such as JWT-based authentication.\nStrong debugging, problem-solving, and performance optimization skills.\nAbility to work independently and collaboratively in remote environments.\nGood written and verbal communication skills.\nPreferred Qualifications\nExperience building AI-powered platforms or recommendation systems.\nFamiliarity with caching systems, async pipelines, or scalable backend workflows.\nExperience with prompt engineering, AI agent design, or LLM integration.\nPortfolio or GitHub projects demonstrating backend or full-stack development skills.\nInterest in modern AI-assisted software development workflows.\n•\n•\n•\n•\n•\n•\n•\n•\n•\n•\n•\n2	jd_pdf	Seyo Job Description Rewritten To Match Cv (1).pdf	processed	{"title": "Backend / Full-stack Developer", "summary": "Remote/contract Backend / Full-stack Developer role focused on building modern web applications with Node.js, Spring Boot, React, RESTful APIs, and SQL/NoSQL databases. The position emphasizes scalable systems, AI-powered features, performance optimization, and collaboration with distributed teams in a remote, agile environment.", "required_skills": [{"name": "Node.js", "canonical": "node_js", "source": "llm_structured", "section_origin": "summary", "aliases": ["node.js", "nodejs", "node"], "confidence": 0.99, "importance": 5, "requirement_t