27	Senior AI Engineer	Experienced AI Engineer role focused on AI, Big Data, IoT, and process automation to drive digital transformation through innovative technology solutions.	CNN\nRNN\nYOLO\nTransformer\nBERT\nT5\nNatural Language Processing\nOptical Character Recognition\nImage Analysis\nText Analysis\nData Preprocessing\ndatabase relationships\nACID transactions\ndata consistency\nONNX\nTFLite\nTensorRT\nArtificial Intelligence\nMachine Learning\nModel Optimization\nGit\nGitLab\nCI/CD\nDocker\nMLOps\nMLflow\nClearML\nBig Data\nInternet of Things\nprocess automation\nAI/ML R&D\nsoftware design patterns\nmicroservices architecture\nscalable AI systems\nSoftware Development\ndigital transformation	draft	2026-05-15 07:06:11.426318+00	2026-05-15 07:06:11.434639+00	Architect the future with strategic roadmaps and visionary planning\nDeliver next-gen solutions centered on AI platforms; IoT smart automation is an added advantage\nExplore emerging tech trends and translate insights into competitive advantages\nCollaborate across departments to turn prototypes into commercial successes\nEnsure top-tier quality, reliability, and creativity in every solution\nAdvise senior management with clear progress updates and strategic insights	Bachelor’s or Master’s in Computer Science, Data Science, or related field\n5–7+ years in AI/ML R&D\nHands-on with CNN, RNN, YOLO, Transformer, BERT, T5\nStrong in data preprocessing, NLP, OCR, image/text analysis\nProficient with Git/GitLab, CI/CD, Docker, MLOps (MLflow, ClearML)\nSkilled in model optimization (ONNX, TFLite, TensorRT)\nExperience with Microservices architecture for scalable AI systems\nKnowledge of database relationships, ACID transactions, and data consistency\nAbility to apply software design patterns for clean, reusable code	Senior AI Engineer\ncareerviet.vn/vi/tim-viec-lam/senior-ai-engineer.35C742E5.html\nDIGI-TEXX Vietnam\nNgày cập nhật\n11/05/2026\nNgành nghề\nCNTT - Phần mềm\nHình thức\nNhân viên chính thức\nLương\nCạnh tranh\nKinh nghiệm\n5 - 10 Năm\nCấp bậc\nNhân viên\nHết hạn nộp\n31/05/2026\nPhúc lợi\nLaptop\nChế độ bảo hiểm\nDu Lịch\nChế độ thưởng\nChăm sóc sức khỏe\nĐào tạo\nTăng lương\n1/3\n\nCông tác phí\nNghỉ phép năm\nCLB thể thao\nMô tả Công việc\nWe’re looking for an experienced AI Engineer to create innovative technology solutions,\nfocusing on areas such as Artificial Intelligence (AI), Big Data, Internet of Things (IoT), and\nprocess automation. This role requires a blend of deep technical expertise and strategic\nthinking to drive digital transformation initiatives.\nWorking location: 2nd Floor, Anna Building, Quang Trung Software City, District 12, HCMC\nWorking time: Monday to Friday\nWhat You’ll Own & Drive\nArchitect the future with strategic roadmaps and visionary planning\nDeliver next-gen solutions centered on AI platforms; IoT smart automation is an added\nadvantage\nExplore emerging tech trends and translate insights into competitive advantages\nCollaborate across departments to turn prototypes into commercial successes\nEnsure top-tier quality, reliability, and creativity in every solution\nAdvise senior management with clear progress updates and strategic insights\nYêu Cầu Công Việc\nBachelor’s or Master’s in Computer Science, Data Science, or related field\n5–7+ years in AI/ML R&D\nHands-on with CNN, RNN, YOLO, Transformer, BERT, T5\nStrong in data preprocessing, NLP, OCR, image/text analysis\nProficient with Git/GitLab, CI/CD, Docker, MLOps (MLflow, ClearML)\nSkilled in model optimization (ONNX, TFLite, TensorRT)\nExperience with Microservices architecture for scalable AI systems\nKnowledge of database relationships, ACID transactions, and data consistency\nAbility to apply software design patterns for clean, reusable code\nĐịa điểm làm việc\nTầng 2, Anna Building, Công viên phần mềm Quang Trung, P. Trung Mỹ Tây\nThông tin khác\nBằng cấp: Đại học\nĐộ tuổi: Không giới hạn tuổi\nLương: Cạnh tranh\n2/3\n\n3/3	jd_pdf	careerviet.vn-Senior AI Engineer.pdf	p